d-force per Square Inch (psi)</strong></h2>



<p>A pound-force per square inch (symbol: psi) is a unit of pressure used i=
n the imperial and US customary systems. It represents the pressure resulti=
ng from a force of one pound-force applied over an area of one square inch.=
</p>



